                     <origDate notBefore="1916" notAfter="1917">The colophon mentions Queen Zäwditu
                        (r. 1916-30, crowned in 1917).
 King Mǝnilǝk II (r. 1889-1913) is
                        mentioned on <locus target="#53ra">53ra</locus> and Metropolitan Ṗeṭros (in
                        tenure in 1883-1917) on <locus target="#53rb">53rb</locus>. On <locus target="#143ra">143ra</locus>, Patriarch Qerǝllos of Alexandria (Cyril V,
                        r. 1874-1927) is mentioned. The reason for mentioning Mǝnilǝk is
                        unclear.</origDate>
